{
  "stem": "18670.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 405.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were fed better too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't know whether they had a guilt complex.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was never too much talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing is that when they got back to my Mainz, they started to demand a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did they get back-- how did you get them back?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We brought them back by truck, American Army truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they have on their backs, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we had nothing to do with them after this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was taken over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just disappeared within the town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess they had neighbors they must have known from before and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- they got-- it was a different department of our outfit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We gave them apartments that had been confiscated from the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And originally when-- the first time when we moved out Germans out of the area that we occupied, there was one family was this fellow who had survived with his wife and son.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came out and told my commanding officer, he is a survivor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, the Germans are in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tell them to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I told them to get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No they were not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their general behavior.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when you started thinking-- later on you start to think about it, you say to yourself, would I have been any different?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at first, it's a shock, because what they have been through, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you're not used to the kind of behavior.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
